{"tid":901812,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"激戰陳瀅 洪永城陰陰笑：喺水缸","createTime":"2018-11-14T09:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T05:03:16.000Z","uid":82917,"like":65,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8c082d7759dc1680b7726cc42d59c66829c8ffd3","tid":901812,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心碎！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藝人陳瀅與洪永城（Tony）到將軍澳電視城出席新劇《黃金有罪》拜神，他們劇中飾演一對情侶，是二人首次有感情戲。 <br />\n<br />\n陳瀅笑指印象中的Tony很Nice，誰知道對方主動約對戲時，竟是約她去跑步！Tony笑說：「跑完步腦筋會清醒啲，方便去諗劇本嘛！（嫌陳瀅身材唔夠好？）唔係，我覺得我身形可以再結實啲，佢就好適合70年代，當年鍾意有少少肉，佢咁樣就最吸引！」 <br />\n<br />\n陳瀅自爆與Tony有很多身體語言作溝通，笑指跑步亦是一個鍛煉方法！問到二人可有床戲？Tony笑言：「正常纏綿啦！喺水缸！我哋有啲70年代艷舞，都幾貼身。」Tony為保持身形，因此經常跑步及練舞。問到Tony的舞技？陳瀅說：「我係排舞室練時都冇人笑！點知佢一入嚟跳啲人就笑唔停！」Tony則笑言要透過跳舞逗人笑，被取笑跳「開心舞」。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXBQGyx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXBQGyx.png&h=2fdd4d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘻，洪仔仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKC8tdA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKC8tdA.png&h=d19a212a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7349e442c3901e1598d0e05926f67d3b302c3d","tid":901812,"uid":82917,"like":27,"dislike":39,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:54:06.000Z","msg":"好想同我洪一齊係尖房抽插<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\